references: I. P. Goulden and D. M. Jackson, Combinatorial Enumeration, Wiley, N.Y., 1983,(2.3.14).
formula: G.f.: (x+2)*(2*x^4+8*x^3+36*x^2+31*x+4)/(1-x)^6. Generally, g.f. for k-th column of A046741 is coefficient of y^k in expansion of (1-y)/((1-y-y^2)*(1-y)-(1+y)*x).
